node.text:
With Valentine’s Day coming  up soon... have you make plans already? Looking out for somewhere to bring your date to for a good pcs of Steak 🥩 or pasta? Here is where I have recently checked out that I would love to introduce you to @isteaksdiner located @sunteccity .

iSTEAKS was founded in 2010, and began serving affordable priced steaks 🥩 at its best and they are also popular for its assortment of sharing, pasta, poultry and seafood dishes. 

These are some of their signature dishes we have tried:
🧧CNY Limited Edition🧧Special Bone-in Pork Chop with Golden Pineapple Sauce, Crackling Pineapple Ring & Toasted Walnut Flakes

💋Australia Wagyu MS9+ Tajima Sirloin
💋Porterhouse Australia, Bass Strait 800g
💋Carbonara with Pancetta & Guanciale, Romano Cheese 🧀 
💋Spicy Tomato & Cream Sauce Crab Meat Pasta w Cheese 🧀 
💋Seafood Aglio Olio
💋Escargot
💋Caesar Salad w Grilled Salmon 
💋Agar Agar
💋Jelly Jelly 
💋Pot de Creme
💋Molten Chocolate Cake with Vanilla Ice-Cream
💋Nitro Nanyang Kopi-O & Lemon Tea

There is just too much of good food, drinks & dessert here... I can’t upload with just 10slots on IG, check out my IGS highlights for more...

Affordable, Premium Quality & Good Service... this is what I observed at this venue, don’t say I never share riaos... bring your date here for a marvellous dining experience 💘💘💘

📍iSTEAKS Diner
3 Temasek Blvd
#02-472/473
Singapore 038983

Many thanks to Ken @kenpgl @sghappens for inviting and @isteaksdiner @sunteccity for having us!
